            <content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>A comprehensive guide to help you get started with UI-Kit (<code>@zaisustech/ui-kit</code>) in your React Native project.</p>
<h2 class="anchor anchorTargetStickyNavbar_x4mB" id="installation">Installation<a href="https://zaisustech.github.io/mobile-sdk-document/blog/getting-started-guide#installation" class="hash-link" aria-label="Direct link to Installation" title="Direct link to Installation" translate="no">​</a></h2>
<p>First, you'll need to set up authentication since <code>@zaisustech/ui-kit</code> is a private package hosted on GitHub Packages. Follow our <a class="" href="https://zaisustech.github.io/mobile-sdk-document/docs/installation">installation guide</a> for detailed steps.</p>
<h2 class="anchor anchorTargetStickyNavbar_x4mB" id="basic-setup">Basic Setup<a href="https://zaisustech.github.io/mobile-sdk-document/blog/getting-started-guide#basic-setup" class="hash-link" aria-label="Direct link to Basic Setup" title="Direct link to Basic Setup" translate="no">​</a></h2>
<p>Once installed, wrap your app with the required providers:</p>
